action.description: Taken from Secretary's desk. Placed on General File.Read third time. Amended. (Amend. No. 940.)Reprinting dispensed with.Read third time. Passed, as amended. Title approved, as amended. (Yeas: 19, Nays: None, Excused: 2.) To printer.From printer. To re-engrossment. Re-engrossed. Second reprint. To Assembly.In Assembly.Read first time. Referred to Committee on Ways and Means. To committee.
